CI rebuild trigger
==================

This file exists to bump the commit SHA on the active asterisk
development branch and re-trigger the CI image build pipeline. It
has no runtime effect and can be safely overwritten on every
rebuild trigger.

Last triggered: 2026-05-17
Reason: ship POST /control/sip/agents/<id>/credentials in
        deploy/control_api.py (commit 44a2318) so the per-agent
        WebRTC softphone can actually register, and click-to-dial
        can find the agent endpoint instead of 409'ing.
